    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Critical enthusiast-grade maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul and reinforcement of the rear subframe to maintain chassis integrity. The suspension is sorted with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and communicative feedback inherent to the platform. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
